cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with image-based virtual try-on for fashion, which involves computer vision and graphics tasks such as warping, texture transfer, and segmentation. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also introduces novel loss functions and training strategies, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.GR (Graphics), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves generating realistic images, which could also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
